126	  
127	  \leanok
128	  This is a formal consequence of the biproduct universal property, preadditivity, and the pullback equation \(X_1 \to X_2 \to X_4 = X_1 \to X_3 \to X_4\). Every step is independent of the value category and transfers verbatim from the abelian-group-valued setting.
